<table class="wikitable floatright" style="text-align:center">
<caption>Example 1 of a microsurvey
</caption>
<tbody><tr>
<td><big>Do you want to try out the<br/>new Example feature?</big>
<p><span class="oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-buttonElement oo-ui-buttonElement-framed oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-buttonWidget" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right: 0.5em;"><span class="oo-ui-buttonElement-button" style="color: #008c6d;border: solid 1px #cdcdcd;margin: 0.1em 0;padding: 0.2em 0.8em;border-radius: 2px;transition: background 0.1s ease-in-out,color 0.1s ease-in-out,box-shadow 0.1s ease-in-out;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;cursor: pointer;"><span class="oo-ui-labelElement-label" style="line-height: 1.9em;">Yes</span></span></span><span class="oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-buttonElement oo-ui-buttonElement-framed oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-buttonWidget" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right: 0.5em;"><span class="oo-ui-buttonElement-button" style="color: #757575;border: solid 1px #cdcdcd;margin: 0.1em 0;padding: 0.2em 0.8em;border-radius: 2px;transition: background 0.1s ease-in-out,color 0.1s ease-in-out,box-shadow 0.1s ease-in-out;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;text-align: center;cursor: pointer;"><span class="oo-ui-labelElement-label" style="line-height: 1.9em;">No</span></span></span>
</p><p><small><span style="text-align:right; color: #757575"><a href="/wiki/Example" class="mw-redirect" title="Example">About this question</a></span></small>
